body:
@onurkaraman : Thanks for the patch. A couple of comments.

1. Since none of the topics is available until the broker has received the first UpdateMetadataRequest. Perhaps we could add a method like isMetadataReady() in MetadataCache. isMetadataReady() is only true after the first UpdateMetadataRequest is received. If isMetadataReady() is false, we just return UnknownTopic to MetadataRequest.

2. We already cache brokerId and rack in MetadataCache. We could just use the cached data in AdminUtils.createTopic(), instead of reading the broker metadata from ZK.
